<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17707499-vanished"><img alt="Vanished: The Sixty-Year Search for the Missing Men of World War II" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1367785757l/17707499._SX98_.jpg" />
